	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When using the debug mode on Nintendulator 0.960 it is way to large for my screen and slows gameplay.  How do you get it to be small like it used to be?
<br />
<br />thank You
<br />
<br />matthew

		

		</td>
